00:32:09,280 --> 00:32:11,280
What is the speed of light?

496
00:32:11,280 --> 00:32:13,280
Three times ten to the eighth something.

497
00:32:13,280 --> 00:32:15,280
But if I change from centimeters to meters,

498
00:32:15,280 --> 00:32:16,280
or meters to centimeters,

