513
00:32:52,280 --> 00:32:54,280
That is what replaces the statement

514
00:32:54,280 --> 00:32:57,280
that the speed of light is three times ten to the eighth

515
00:32:57,280 --> 00:33:00,280
meters per second for all speeds of light.

