00:33:06,280 --> 00:33:08,280
They move on what we call a null trajectory.

519
00:33:08,280 --> 00:33:11,280
A null trajectory means that the proper time

520
00:33:11,280 --> 00:33:14,280
along the trajectory is exactly zero.

521
00:33:14,280 --> 00:33:18,280
That's the universal statement for all light rays,

