00:37:20,280 --> 00:37:22,280
there's complete consensus about it.

610
00:37:22,280 --> 00:37:25,280
Black holes in time evaporate.

611
00:37:25,280 --> 00:37:28,280
If black holes in time evaporate,

612
00:37:28,280 --> 00:37:29,280
then the question is,

613
00:37:29,280 --> 00:37:33,280
what happened to all the little itsy-bitsy bits of information

