00:37:46,280 --> 00:37:50,280
Or does it get radiated out with the evaporation products?

619
00:37:50,280 --> 00:37:55,280
Exactly what happens, this was a big puzzle in physics.

620
00:37:55,280 --> 00:37:57,280
But before we can address the puzzle,

