00:38:04,280 --> 00:38:08,280
before we do that, we have to understand why people thought that black holes,

623
00:38:08,280 --> 00:38:11,280
why people think that black holes evaporate.

624
00:38:11,280 --> 00:38:21,280
Now, a black hole is the most dull object in the universe.

625
00:38:21,280 --> 00:38:25,280
If you create the black hole and leave it for a while,

626
00:38:25,280 --> 00:38:27,280
it settles down to a black hole.

