00:38:55,280 --> 00:38:56,280
Let's call them dead.

635
00:38:56,280 --> 00:38:57,280
Dead in the sense that they're not dead.

636
00:38:57,280 --> 00:39:02,280
In the sense that they are infinitely cold,

