00:40:36,280 --> 00:40:42,280
that eventually they will simply disappear because they'll radiate away all their energy.

660
00:40:42,280 --> 00:40:47,280
And if that happens, as I said, there's the puzzle of what happened to everything that fell in, basically.

661
00:40:47,280 --> 00:40:49,280
Okay.

