00:41:19,280 --> 00:41:21,280
We're going to go through Bekenstein's arguments

669
00:41:22,280 --> 00:41:25,280
about why black holes have to have entropy.

670
00:41:25,280 --> 00:41:28,280
Now first, before we talk about why black holes have entropy,

